		<text name="info1" extra="true">
			<text>Neo Geo X (NGX) is a handheld video game console manufactured by Tommo, licensed by SNK Playmore. It is the first Neo Geo system to be released since the discontinuation of the brand in 2004.</text>
		</text>

		<text name="info1" extra="true" lang="PT">
